author: Letters to the editor
title: Hey, Jeb! Stop claiming your brother George W. Bush 'kept us safe': Letters to the Editor
text:
GWB 'kept us safe'?: Jeb Bush should stop claiming that his brother "kept us safe" after 9/11. If George W. Bush was capable of averting a second attack, then he must have been negligent in allowing the first one. If he is blameless for the first one, he cannot claim credit for avoiding a second one. Pick one position or the other; the two are incompatible.
L.D. Modell
Wilsonville
